# <%= @current_collective.name %>'s Funding Pool

Each LLM call an attached agent makes is billed to one enrolled member's own prepaid balance, chosen at random per call, so cost spreads evenly across enrolled members over time. The pool never holds money.
<% if @funding_pool.archived? %>

**This pool is closed.** Its agents are suspended and no balances are being drawn on. Enrollments are kept in case it reopens; withdrawal is still available.
<% elsif !@funding_pools_enabled %>

**Funding pools are currently disabled for this collective.** No balances are being drawn on; enrollment is paused. Withdrawal is still available.
<% end %>

| | |
|---------|-------|
| Status | <%= @funding_pool.archived? ? "Closed" : "Open" %> |
| Member daily draw ceiling | <%= @funding_pool.member_daily_draw_cap_cents ? format("$%.2f per member per day (UTC)", @funding_pool.member_daily_draw_cap_cents / 100.0) : "(none)" %> |
| Enrolled members | <%= @pool_enrollments.any? ? @pool_enrollments.map { |e| "[#{e.user.display_name}](#{e.user.path})" }.join(", ") : "(none yet)" %> |
| Funded agents | <%= @funded_agents.any? ? @funded_agents.map { |a| "[#{a.display_name}](#{a.path})" }.join(", ") : "(none yet)" %> |
| Your enrollment | <%= @current_user_enrolled ? "Enrolled — this pool's agents can draw from your prepaid balance" : "Not enrolled" %> |

Enrolling is consenting to fund this collective's agents from your own prepaid balance; it requires active billing with prepaid credits, and you can withdraw at any time. Withdrawal drops you out of draws immediately. Admins manage the pool itself (lifecycle, draw ceiling, attached agents) from the collective's settings.
